2024 00:41:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-spikes-spectre-intervention-spooks-investors-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>台积电将公布强劲利润，但特朗普言论重挫其股价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-set-report-strong-profit-stock-pressured-by-trump-comments-2024-07-18/</link><description>人工智能 (AI) 应用芯片的主要制造商台积电预计周四将再次公布强劲的季度收益，但受唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 对台湾言论的压力，其台北股价下跌 4%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 00:03:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tsmc-set-report-strong-profit-stock-pressured-by-trump-comments-2024-07-18/</guid></item><item><title>向俄罗斯走私军事技术的男子被判入狱三年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/man-who-smuggled-military-tech-russia-sentenced-3-years-us-jail-2024-07-17/</link><description>美国司法部表示，一名俄罗斯男子周三被判处三年监禁，该男子承认美国指控他向俄罗斯走私大量美国制造的军用级微电子产品。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:59:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/man-who-smuggled-military-tech-russia-sentenced-3-years-us-jail-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>早盘买盘：随着科技股下跌、日元飙升，波动性回归</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-17/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:49:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普国家安全顾问呼吁台湾增加国防开支</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-national-security-adviser-calls-taiwan-lift-defense-spending-2024-07-17/</link><description>唐纳德·特朗普的一位高级国家安全顾问周三表示，面对中国潜在的侵略，台湾需要大幅增加国防开支。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:44:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/trump-national-security-adviser-calls-taiwan-lift-defense-spending-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国高级代表团强调巴布亚新几内亚的承诺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/high-level-us-delegation-stresses-papua-new-guinea-commitment-2024-07-17/</link><description>美国高级民事和军事代表团本周访问了巴布亚新几内亚，强调美国对中国正在争夺影响力的太平洋战略领土的承诺。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 21:01:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/high-level-us-delegation-stresses-papua-new-guinea-commitment-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示已停止与美国就台湾问题进行军控谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-it-has-halted-arms-control-talks-with-us-over-taiwan-2024-07-17/</link><description>中国外交部周三表示，中国已停止与美国展开的核军控谈判，以抗议华盛顿向民主治理的台湾岛出售武器，北京声称台湾是其领土。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 18:06:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-says-it-has-halted-arms-control-talks-with-us-over-taiwan-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>香港记者小组负责人表示，她因新闻自由争议而被《华尔街日报》解雇</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-journalist-group-head-says-she-was-fired-by-wsj-amid-press-freedom-row-2024-07-17/</link><description>香港记者协会(HKJA)会长表示，周三，她被《华尔街日报》解雇，原因是她拒绝了该报高级编辑提出的与该组织断绝关系、不再倡导媒体自由的要求。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 15:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-journalist-group-head-says-she-was-fired-by-wsj-amid-press-freedom-row-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国西南部购物中心火灾已造成16人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/least-six-killed-southwest-china-shopping-centre-fire-state-media-reports-2024-07-17/</link><description>官方媒体周四称，周三晚间中国西南部四川省一家百货商店发生火灾，造成 16 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 14:50:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/least-six-killed-southwest-china-shopping-centre-fire-state-media-reports-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>七国集团贸易部长就解决不公平贸易问题加强对话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-trade-ministers-toughen-talk-tackling-unfair-trade-2024-07-17/</link><description>七国集团（G7）主要民主国家的贸易部长周三表示，如果需要的话，他们将使用“贸易工具”来对抗扭曲市场的做法，与之前的公报相比，措辞更加强硬。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 13:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/g7-trade-ministers-toughen-talk-tackling-unfair-trade-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织称中国的产业支持计划缺乏透明度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-support-programmes-lack-transparency-wto-says-2024-07-17/</link><description>世界贸易组织周三表示，由于“总体缺乏透明度”，它无法清楚了解中国对电动汽车或铝和钢铁生产等关键工业部门的财政支持。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 12:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-industrial-support-programmes-lack-transparency-wto-says-2024-07-17/</guid></item><item><title>纳斯达克、标准普尔 500 指数收盘大幅走低，受筹码、大盘股冲击；道指延续涨势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/wall-st-futures-slump-after-rally-tech-stocks-slide-2024-07-17/</link><description>标准普尔 500 指数和纳斯达克指数周三暴跌，因中美贸易冲突可能升级，微芯片股暴跌，加剧了大型科技相关股票的持续轮动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Jul 2024 10:17:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/wall-st-futures-slump-after-rally-tech-stocks-slide-2024-07-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>